	   |     |     |     |     |     |     |     |     |
	   |     |     |     |     |     |     |     |     |
	   |     |     |     |     |     |     |     |     |
	   | WP  | WP  | WP  | WP  | WP  | WP  | WP  | WP  |
	   | WR  | WKn | WB  | WQ  | WK  | WB  | WKn | WR  |
	Then the piece at (2,1) should have exactly the following moves
         | X | Y |
         | 1 | 3 |
         | 3 | 3 |
	And the piece at (7,1) should have exactly the following moves
		| X | Y |
		| 6 | 3 |
		| 8 | 3 |

